										(4)





										4 X 4
										(9)





										5 X 5
										(2)









Corners



X
Hinge Corners



Hinges with rounded corners can easily be identified by comparing them to the radius of a US Dime or Quarter. 1/4 Inch Radius Hinges match up very closely with the radius of the Dime, and 5/8 Inch Radius Hinges match up very well with the Quarter. Square corner hinges have sharp cornered points.







										1/4" Radius Corner
										(4)





										5/8" Radius Corner
										(4)





										Square Corner
										(15)









Color



X
